      • get__pointer

        public int get__pointer()
        Do not use: If you need a primary-key ID of this Topic, use Topic#getTopicCode() instead. This is only useful when ordering topics during the creation of a Dataset.
        Returns:
        the ID element of the Topic that is used in the response document. Actually an internal pointer that links topics and items together when SOAP serialized.
